# lychee allow-list — broken links we accept on purpose.
#
# Each line is a regex matched against the FULL URL (lychee semantics).
# Add a comment explaining WHY before each pattern.

# docs.rs URLs for unpublished or not-yet-published luna-* versions.
# Pre-publish: these 404 because the crate version isn't on crates.io yet.
# Post-publish (Phase G ship): remove this allow-list entry — verify links
# resolve. See `.dev/rfcs/v2.0-plan-state.md` Track DO-CI for context.
^https://docs\.rs/luna-[a-z-]+/(latest|\d+(\.\d+)*)/.*$
